  <h2>Why Homeowners Choose Zaricci for AGA Appliance Repair</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Experienced with Luxury AGA Appliances:</strong> We work on premium cooking appliances and understand the unique construction, heat retention, controls, and performance expectations that come with AGA ownership.</li>
    <li><strong>Focused Diagnostic Approach:</strong> We do not treat an AGA like a standard range. Our service is centered on identifying the actual cause of heating problems, control issues, ignition faults, and performance irregularities before recommending repair.</li>
    <li><strong>Repair, Installation & Maintenance:</strong> In addition to <strong>AGA repair</strong>, we also provide <strong>AGA appliance installation</strong> and <strong>AGA appliance maintenance</strong> to help protect long-term performance.</li>
    <li><strong>Clear Communication:</strong> You receive straightforward recommendations, transparent pricing, and a defined repair plan before work begins.</li>
    <li><strong>Luxury Home Service Experience:</strong> We provide careful service designed for premium kitchens, custom cabinetry, and high-end homes throughout Los Angeles and surrounding communities.</li>
  </ul>
